### EduPortal API - Counseling Controller
### Counseling session management endpoints (Not fully implemented)
### Base URL: http://localhost:5000
### Requires Authentication

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/counseling
@contentType = application/json
@token = {{$dotenv TOKEN}}

### ===========================================
### GET ALL COUNSELING SESSIONS - (Admin, Danışman)
### Note: Service not yet implemented
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET SESSION BY ID
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET SESSIONS BY STUDENT
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/student/1?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET SESSIONS BY COUNSELOR - (Admin, Danışman)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/counselor/1?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET UPCOMING SESSIONS
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/upcoming
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### CREATE SESSION - (Admin, Danışman)
### ===========================================
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "studentId": 1,
  "counselorId": 1,
  "scheduledDate": "2024-12-15T10:00:00Z",
  "type": "Academic",
  "notes": "Akademik performans değerlendirmesi"
}

### ===========================================
### UPDATE SESSION - (Admin, Danışman)
### ===========================================
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "scheduledDate": "2024-12-16T14:00:00Z",
  "notes": "Güncellenen notlar"
}

### ===========================================
### DELETE SESSION - (Admin only)
### ===========================================
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
